lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps of the United States won the Olympic 200 meters individual medley on Thursday to capture the 22nd gold medal of his career and become the first swimmer to win the same event at four consecutive Games.

headline.main: Phelps Writes Yet More History With IM Win
